<h2><?= __('How to dislay the Joli Table Of Contents ?', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></h2>
<p><?= __('There are several ways to have the table of contents display on your website.', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<h3>1. <?= __('Auto-insert', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></h3>
<p><?= __('Upon activating the plugin the first time, auto-insert is not activated.', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<p><?= __('If you wish to activate it, do as follow:', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<p><?= __('In the Settings page, under the "Auto-Insert" tab, "Post type" option, tick which post type you wish to have the table of contents to automatically display', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<h3>2. <?= __('Using the shortcode', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></h3>
<p><?= __('Use the following shortcode within your content to have the table of contents display where you wish to:', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<p><code>[joli-toc]</code></p>
<h3>3. <?= __('Using the individual post settings', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></h3>
<p><?= __('While editing a post, scroll down below your content until you reach the "Joli Table Of Contents" meta box.', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<p><?= __('From here on, you can either Enable or Disable the Table of Contents. This will override the global settings.', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></p>
<p><span class="warning"><?= __('Do not tick Enable and Disable at the same time or the Table of Contents will remain disabled.', 'joli-table-of-contents'); ?></span></p>